@startuml sequence-license-detention.puml
title Driving License Detention - Sequence Diagram

actor "Licensing Employee" as Employee
boundary "DVLD UI" as UI
control "DetentionService" as DetentionService
database "SQL Server Database" as DB

Employee -> UI : Enter license number and detention details
UI -> DetentionService : Submit detention request
DetentionService -> DB : Validate license number
DB --> DetentionService : License found

DetentionService -> DB : Save detention record
DB --> DetentionService : Detention saved

DetentionService --> UI : Display detention confirmation

@enduml
